                learners are expected to know how to construct a regular heptagon (7-sided polygon) using a compass, ruler, and protractor.
            </p>
            <p xml:id="auto_02j2dyeg">
              Materials Needed:  
            </p>
            <p xml:id="auto_tash7l10">
                <ol xml:id="auto_c661nfw1">
                    <li xml:id="auto_qzu4rswa">
                        <p xml:id="auto_h3zesqus">
                           Materials Needed: </p>
                         <p xml:id="auto_xzn40on0"> â™¦ Compass</p>
                             <p xml:id="auto_x8xzwtcg"> â™¦  Ruler</p>
                            <p xml:id="auto_w5lwdqt9"> â™¦  Protractor</p>
                            <p xml:id="auto_nvwrh621">â™¦  Pencil</p>
                                   
                                    
                                    
                                    <p xml:id="auto_kubyq9m1">â™¦  Eraser</p>  
